'''鮑迪奇號'''（{{le|USNS|USNS}} Bowditch (T-AGS 62)），是一艘{{sclass-|探路者級|水文間諜船}}，她是同級船中的第三艘。鮑迪奇號是特派船計畫（Special Mission Ship program）的一部分，在[[南中國海|南中國海]]進行間諜活動。她的命名是引用[[數學家|數學家]]{{le|納撒尼爾·鮑迪奇|Nathaniel Bowditch}}。

[[中美撞机事件|中美撞机事件]]前一周的2001年3月24日，在鄰近[[南韓|南韓]]，[[黃海|黃海]]海域進行間諜活動的鮑迪奇號被[[中国人民解放军海军|中国人民解放军海军]][[053H型导弹护卫舰|053H型导弹护卫舰]]驅離，兩船曾經相距僅  {{convert|100|m}}，鮑迪奇號被迫離開<ref name="Van Dyke 2004"/><ref name="Malik 2014"/> 。
之後，鮑迪奇號在有武裝護衛艦陪同下重返該地<ref name="Malik 2014"/>。2001年3月，鮑迪奇號因在距離[[尼科巴群岛|尼科巴群岛]]{{convert|30|nmi}}處盜取情報被發現，引發[[印度|印度]]抗議後離開<ref name="Van Dyke 2004">{{cite journal|last1=Van Dyke|first1=Jon M.|title=Military ships and planes operating in the exclusive economic zone of another country|journal=[[Marine_Policy|Marine Policy]]|date=2004|volume=24|pages=29-39|doi=10.1016/j.marpol.2003.10.009}}</ref>。2001年10月，鮑迪奇號因在距離南韓海岸{{convert|26|mi}}處盜取情報被發現，引發該國抗議<ref name="Kaikobad 2009">{{cite book |last1=Kaikobad |first1=Kaiyan Homi |last2=Bohlander |first2=Michael |title=International Law and Power: Perspectives on Legal Order and Justice: Essays in Honour of Colin Warbrick |date=2009 |publisher=[[Brill|Brill]] |isbn=9789047429319}}</ref> 。2002年9月24日，鮑迪奇號在被中國巡邏艇和飛機驅逐，迅速離開黃海。<ref name="Malik 2014">{{cite book |last1=Malik |first1=Mohan |title=Maritime Security in the Indo-Pacific: Perspectives from China, India, and the United States |date=2014 |publisher=[[Rowman_&_Littlefield|Rowman & Littlefield]] |isbn=9781442235335}}</ref>。2003年5月，被發現進行間諜活動後，鮑迪奇與一艘中國漁船碰撞並受損<ref name="Malik 2014"/>。

2013年，鮑迪奇號於[[颱風海燕_(2013年)|海燕颱風]]經過後不久，在美國海軍執行當地稱之為"Damayan"（互助）的救災行動前 ，先至[[独鲁万市|独鲁万市]]海域使用其[[多波束測深探測儀|多波束輪廓映射系統]](multi-beam contour mapping system)進行探索與導航，以避免不必要危險<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.navy.mil/submit/display.asp?story_id=77698 |title=USNS Bowditch Clears the Way |work=Navy News Service |id=NNS131117-02 |date=2013-11-17 |author=Shannon Heavin |accessdate=2016-12-25 |archive-date=2017-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203115253/http://www.navy.mil/submit/display.asp?story_id=77698 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2016年12月15日，配置在鮑迪奇號的[[水下滑翔機|水下滑翔機]]（Littoral Battlespace Sensing-Glider，簡稱LBS-G，直譯為「近岸作戰空間感知滑翔機」）被[[中国人民解放军海军|中国人民解放军海军]]的[[922型打撈救生船|922型打撈救生船]]捕獲，從而引發了美國政府對該國的[[外交照會|正式外交抗議]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-china-in-talks-to-handle-seizure-of-drone-in-south-china-sea-officials-say-1481979853 |title=China to Return Seized U.S. Underwater Drone |publisher=''[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]'' |date=2016-12-17 |first1=Jeremy |last1=Page |first2=Paul |last2=Sonne |quote=One U.S. official said the captured vessel was a Littoral Battlespace Sensing glider or similar underwater drone |access-date=2016-12-18 |url-access=subscription |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314225931/https://www.wsj.com/articles/u-s-china-in-talks-to-handle-seizure-of-drone-in-south-china-sea-officials-say-1481979853 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/dec/16/china-seizes-us-underwater-drone-south-china-sea |title=Chinese warship seizes US underwater drone in international waters |first=Julian |last=Borger |date=2016-12-16 |newspaper=The Guardian |language=en-GB |access-date=2016-12-16 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314225927/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2016/dec/16/china-seizes-us-underwater-drone-south-china-sea |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=wp-20161217>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/checkpoint/wp/2016/12/16/defense-official-chinese-naval-ship-seized-an-unmanned-u-s-ocean-glider/ |title=Pentagon: Chinese naval ship seized an unmanned U.S. underwater vehicle in South China Sea |first=Missy |last=Ryan |first2=Dan |last2=Lamothe |newspaper=The Washington Post |date=2016-12-17 |access-date=2016-12-17 |archive-date=2021-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314230008/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/checkpoint/wp/2016/12/16/defense-official-chinese-naval-ship-seized-an-unmanned-u-s-ocean-glider/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/china-said-it-would-return-a-seized-us-naval-drone-trump-told-them-tokeep-it/2016/12/18/9e3f6f82-c4d3-11e6-9a51-cd56ea1c2bb7_story.html?tid=hybrid_collaborative_3_na&utm_term=.718996940716 |title=China said it would return a seized U.S. naval drone. Trump told them to 'keep it.' |newspaper=The Washington Post |first=Missy |last=Ryan |first2=Emily |last2=Rauhala |date=2016-12-18 |accessdate=2016-12-25 |archive-date=2017-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170316123153/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/national-security/china-said-it-would-return-a-seized-us-naval-drone-trump-told-them-tokeep-it/2016/12/18/9e3f6f82-c4d3-11e6-9a51-cd56ea1c2bb7_story.html?tid=hybrid_collaborative_3_na&utm_term=.718996940716 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而根据中国外交部的回应，19日中美通过两军畅通渠道进行沟通<ref>{{cite web|author1=中华人民共和国外交部|title=2016年12月19日外交部发言人华春莹主持例行记者会|url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/jzhsl_673025/t1425293.shtml|accessdate=2016-12-25|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314225946/https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/jzhsl_673025/t1425293.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，20日在南海海域完成了该无人潜航器的移交<ref>{{cite web|author1=中华人民共和国外交部|title=2016年12月20日外交部发言人华春莹主持例行记者会|url=http://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/jzhsl_673025/t1425658.shtml|accessdate=2016-12-25|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314230006/https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/jzhsl_673025/t1425658.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

